MCCGS: Movable Camera Cluster Gaussian Splatting

This repository is derived from and built on top of:

  4DGaussians: 4D Gaussian Splatting for Real-Time Dynamic Scene Rendering
  https://github.com/hustvl/4DGaussians

The original 4DGaussians code is distributed under the Apache License,
Version 2.0. The Apache License text is preserved in LICENSE.md.

MCCGS modifications include movable-camera-cluster dataset handling,
frame-aware timestamps, pose refinement, motion-compensated Gaussian
propagation, and posterior-guided Gaussian completion.

This repository also depends on components from 3D Gaussian Splatting and
its rasterization/simple-knn submodules. Users should check the licenses of
the upstream projects and submodules before redistribution or commercial use.
